{"type": "article", "id": 60084, "title": "让灯光变得柔和的灯罩，是蘑菇菌丝体做的｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-01-08T22:58:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 536, "name": "三星"}, {"id": 55758, "name": "Monica Förster Design"}, {"id": 9442, "name": "Georg Jensen"}, {"id": 3203, "name": "Balenciaga"}, {"id": 55759, "name": "Ruohong Wu"}, {"id": 18170, "name": "Nir Meiri"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 95, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190108192303Pjwm1D2ZYp8bnofq.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #2965a8; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #2965a8} span.s6 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #2965a8; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #2965a8} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} span.s8 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>The Sustainable Lamps by Nir Meiri </h3><p>居住在伦敦的设计师 Nir Meiri 创造了一系列使用蘑菇菌丝体制作的台灯，作为合成材料的替代品。台灯的灯罩部分由菌丝体制成，支架和底座部分则用了常规的金属材料。</p><p>光源从底座部分向上照亮，投射到菌丝体制作的灯罩上，营造出柔和自然的光照效果。</p><p>这是 Nir Meiri 与伦敦创业公司 Biohm 合作生产的结果，后者致力于为建筑环境提供可持续解决方案，每个灯罩都是将完全干燥后的菌丝体压成扁平状后制作而成的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192505o1WrK0FqN9LUbk2V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192333IMgviD9Xf4pbE0z6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.553299\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192334wu795p0mBaFKgxQM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.109137\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192335Rtisc8lhIek9Z7va.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192429P8cT3LAbhVo5Flem.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/01/07/nir-meiri-mycelium-lamps-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>All Different All Equal by Ruohong Wu</h3><p>居住在鹿特丹的中国艺术家 Ruohong Wu 创造了一系列造型独特的瓷器，意在为“中国制造”赋予新的含义。</p><p>为了证明大规模生产的物品也可以有个性，Ruohong Wu 使用从中国街头采集的重组模具制作了一系列滑铸瓷器。这个名为 All Different All Equal 的项目，灵感源自她的景德镇之旅。她在那里发现了大量废弃的工厂、苦苦挣扎的制造商和布满街头小巷的廉价纪念品。</p><p>她收集了大量被丢弃的经典陶瓷铸件，都是些通常用于大规模生产的模具，她将各种不匹配的部件连接在一起，创造了一系列独特的混合体，展示了大规模生产中个性化的可能性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192537OXIKGCz1Zh2gYLf6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192538k1UWdlYmv9IV2zKo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192539LsmUVyA1dcJnTqEh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192539brihgTdy0UCRo8lZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192540B04frJ3DTXWAm2Es.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://ruohongwu.com/all-different-all-equal\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ruohong Wu</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Balenciaga's First Kering Eyewear Collection</h3><p>Balenciaga 创意总监 Demna Gvasalia 最近与 Kering Eyewear 合作推出了 Balenciaga 的首个眼镜系列。整个系列混合了锐舞文化、滑雪装备、经典眼镜造型，产品种类丰富，将在 Dover Street Market 独家发售。</p><p>其中几个款式的设计非常前卫独特，适合先锋人士的造型搭配，包括一款猫眼造型的隐形镜框，和 Oversized 蝴蝶眼镜。目前，Balenciaga 首个眼镜系列已在纽约、伦敦、东京、新加坡、洛杉矶、北京各地的 Dover Street Market 上架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192639L7v6YJWGw923zX4P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192640BYCtr4xP5yz2cdvS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192640Q0i3WOMwLDuqaSog.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192641jrJNBki86zsvg2S4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192642zXrJRl7jBmiuS5AO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192642zMBnYWSdtc1PCUqF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192643m2LRF17O9TU8Y364.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192643nSeCzcRNhq53A8bm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Matrix Collection by Monica Förster Design for Georg Jensen </h3><p>丹麦设计品牌 Georg Jensen 与瑞典设计师 Monica Förster 合作，推出了 Matrix 系列新品。</p><p>这个装饰艺术风格的新系列包括两个圆柱形花瓶，两个方形花瓶、两个碗和一个托盘。新品由不锈钢制成，采用方形网格设计，赋予每件作品雕塑化的外观。</p><p>花瓶上的相同网格也出现在碗的底部和托盘的周边上，为整体设计增添了一点视觉亮度。你可以将花朵、铅笔和刷子单独地或是成组地放置在穿孔网格中，以形成独特的桌面装饰。售价 60 美元起，<a href=\"https://www.georgjensen.com/en-us/search?q=matrix&amp;prefn1=ProductCollection&amp;pmin=1.00&amp;prefv1=Matrix\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192729z2ja6enAyHIU3Go5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192729rWGNkUPfH8I94YEb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192730pQWyoAi1zYnKTHdw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333594\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192830fmlxv3YcISOA0QaV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.189062\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192831amRf9XJkrsFeh2cg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.129687\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Samsung Space Monitor</h3><p>在最新的 CES 2019 展会上，三星将推出一款名为 Space Monitor 的显示器新品，亮点是可以大大节省桌面空间。</p><p>Space 采用臂夹支架来连接到桌子的背面，不使用时，它可以旋转 180 度，将显示器朝向墙面。Space 显示器有 27 英寸以及 32 英寸两个版本可供选择，27 英寸的分辨率为 2K(GHD2560×1440)，32 英寸的分辨率为 4K(UHD3840×2160)。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192859yZNPgTC1YKRiEaxe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192859HsIC9PRi0NYfWxDw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192900eOVd8M7koS9A3YKL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192900qcEW6L1BYXsZ2HAm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190108192900lQCkg314LMEJyWRj.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/samsung-space-monitor-declutters-desk-space/space_monitor_1-2/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">&nbsp;</p>"}